# Retrui Environment Variables

# ======================
# OPTIONAL CONFIGURATION
# ======================

# Google Search Console Verification
# Get this from Google Search Console -> Settings -> Ownership verification
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION=

# ======================
# DEPLOYMENT
# ======================

# Rust API URL (required for production)
# Development: Not needed, Next.js proxies to localhost:8080
# Production: Set to your deployed Rust API URL
# RUST_API_URL=https://retrui-api.fly.dev

# Production URL (automatically set by Vercel)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://retrui.vercel.app

# ======================
# NOTES
# ======================

# This project requires NO environment variables for basic functionality.
# All features work out of the box with default settings.
#
# For production deployment on Vercel:
# 1. Fork this repository
# 2. Import to Vercel
# 3. Deploy!
#
# Analytics data will be automatically available in your Vercel dashboard
# after the first deployment.
